# Project Architecture

## Overview

pnpm workspace monorepo with Turbo, hosting a Next.js 15 (App Router) DEX web application. Heavily depends on `@liberfi.io/*` packages from the sibling `react-sdk` repo.

## Monorepo Structure

| Layer | Path | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| App | `apps/web/` | Next.js 15 application (App Router) |
| Core utils | `packages/core/` | Shared utilities, config, types |
| Locales | `packages/locales/` | i18n translations (gulp build) |
| Data hooks | `packages/react-backend/` | GraphQL client |
| Data hooks | `packages/react-dex/` | DEX API hooks |
| Data hooks | `packages/react-launchpad/` | Launchpad hooks |
| Data hooks | `packages/react-redpacket/` | RedPacket hooks |
| UI | `packages/ui-base/` | Base UI components |
| UI | `packages/ui-dex/` | DEX-specific UI |
| UI | `packages/ui-launchpad/` | Launchpad UI |
| UI | `packages/ui-redpacket/` | RedPacket UI |

## Tech Stack

| Concern | Choice |
|---------|--------|
| Language | TypeScript 5.7 |
| Framework | Next.js 15 (App Router) |
| Package manager | pnpm 9.5.0 |
| Build orchestration | Turbo |
| State management | Jotai + TanStack React Query 5 |
| UI library | HeroUI + Tailwind CSS 4 + Framer Motion |
| Authentication | Privy (`@liberfi.io/wallet-connector-privy`) |
| Blockchain | `@chainstream-io/sdk`, Solana Web3, viem |
| i18n | next-international + i18next + `@liberfi.io/i18n` |
| Monitoring | Sentry (`@sentry/nextjs`) |
| GraphQL | graphql-request + graphql-codegen |

## Routing (App Router)

Route groups separate new and legacy implementations:

| Group | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `app/(new)/` | New layout and pages |
| `app/(legacy)/` | Legacy pages using older providers |

Key routes:

| Route | Page |
|-------|------|
| `/` | Discovery (token list) |
| `/tokens/[[...slug]]` | Token detail |
| `/predict` | Prediction market list |
| `/predict/[id]` | Prediction detail |
| `/channels`, `/channels/[id]` | Signal channels |
| `/portfolio` | Portfolio |
| `/redpacket` | RedPacket |
| `/discover` | Discovery |

## Provider Hierarchy

```
QueryClientProvider
└─ AuthProviders (Privy)
    └─ LocaleProvider
        └─ ServiceProviders
            ├─ DexClientProvider / APIClientProvider
            ├─ MediaTrackProvider
            ├─ ChannelsProvider
            ├─ PredictProvider
            └─ PortfolioProvider
                └─ LegacyBridge
                    └─ PageShell (Scaffold)
```

When adding new providers, insert them at the **ServiceProviders** level.

## Module Singleton Guarantee

`next.config.mjs` uses webpack aliases to ensure monorepo-wide singletons for Jotai, @liberfi.io/ui-chain-select, etc. When adding a new package that holds global state, add its alias to `next.config.mjs` → `resolve.alias`.

## Relationship to react-sdk

- `@liberfi.io/*` packages come from the sibling `../react-sdk` monorepo
- Version source of truth: `../react-sdk/packages/*/package.json`
- When upgrading `@liberfi.io/*`, update ALL workspace packages (apps + packages) — see `.cursor/rules/liberfi-sdk-context.mdc`
- `@liberfi/*` (this repo) wraps and extends `@liberfi.io/*` (react-sdk) for template-specific needs

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS 4 via `@tailwindcss/postcss`
- Global styles: `apps/web/src/styles/globals.css`
- `@source` directives in `globals.css` scan package dist files for class detection
- UI packages produce their own CSS via PostCSS
